esomeListRepo":"0xnr/awesome-bigdata","categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Visualization</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash\">Dash</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/plotly/dash\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">16.5k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":16532,\"repo\":\"plotly/dash\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Analytical Web Apps for Python, R, Julia, and Jupyter. Built on top of plotly, no JS required</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-11T10:26:46.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"newTendermint/awesome-bigdata","categoryHTML":"<h2>Scheduling</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jhuckaby/Cronicle\">Cronicle</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jhuckaby/Cronicle\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.6k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1608,\"repo\":\"jhuckaby/Cronicle\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Distributed, easy to install, NodeJS based, task scheduler</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-11T10:26:46.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo"