ode in the initialization file.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-11T10:20:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ildoc/awesome-italy-events","categoryHTML":"<h2>February</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>11-12 - <a href=\"https://shipping-40.sharevent.it/\">Shipping 4.0</a> - Online - Technology improvements in shipping sector.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-11T08:42:37.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ildoc/awesome-italy-events","categoryHTML":"<h2>March</h2>","itemHTML":"<li>23-25 - <a href=\"https://events.codemotion.com/conferences/online/2021/online-tech-conference-italian-edition-spring/\">Codemotion Online tech conference 2021</a> - Online - Biggest tech conference in Italy.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-11T08:40:42.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"DopplerHQ/awesome-interview-questions","categoryHTML":"<h2>Programming Languages/Frameworks/Platforms</h2><h3>Python</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.careerride.com/python-interview-questions.aspx\">20 Python interview questions and answers</a></li>","updatedAt":"2021-02-11T05:44:31.000Z"}]}},"pageContext":{"type":"day","from":1613001600000,"to":1613087999999,"previousId":"2021-02-12","nextId":"2021-02-10","nextName":"Feb 10th, 2021","previousName":"Feb 12th, 2021"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}